column6: This subclass includes:- passenger transportation services by air on pre-determined international routes and on pre-determined schedules supplied in aircraft (including helicopters) of any type- transportation of accompanying passenger baggage and other items that may be carried at no extra cost

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 64244. International non-scheduled air transport services of passengers
column5: International non-scheduled air transport services of passengers
column6: This subclass includes:- passenger transportation services by air on international routes, on a non-scheduled basis, supplied in aircraft of any type, including helicopters- transportation of accompanying passenger baggage and other items that may be carried at no extra costThis subclass does not include:- sightseeing passenger air transport services, cf. 64134- rental services of passenger aircraft with crew, cf. 66031

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6425. Space transport services of passengers
column5: Space transport services of passengers

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 64250. Space transport services of passengers
column5: Space transport services of passengers
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation of passengers to, from and in outer space by any means

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65. Freight transport services
column5: Freight transport services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 651. Land transport services of freight
column5: Land transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6511. Road transport services of freight
column5: Road transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65111. Road transport services of freight by refrigerator vehicles
column5: Road transport services of freight by refrigerator vehicles
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of frozen or refrigerated goods in specially refrigerated trucks and cars

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65112. Road transport services of freight by tank trucks or semi-trailers
column5: Road transport services of freight by tank trucks or semi-trailers
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of petroleum products (crude oil, natural gas and refined petroleum products) in special tank trucks- transportation by road of other bulk liquids or gases in special tank trucks

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65113. Road transport services of intermodal containers
column5: Road transport services of intermodal containers
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of individual articles and packages assembled and shipped in specially constructed shipping containers designed for ease of handling in transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65114. Road transport services of freight by man- or animal-drawn vehicles
column5: Road transport services of freight by man- or animal-drawn vehicles
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of freight in man- or animal-drawn vehicles

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65115. Moving services of household furniture and household goods
column5: Moving services of household furniture and household goods
column6: This subclass includes:- household goods and furniture removal services- ancillary services, such as packing and carrying and in-house movingThis subclass does not include:- office furniture and equipment removal services, cf. 65119

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65116. Road transport services of letters and parcels
column5: Road transport services of letters and parcels
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation of letters and parcels by any mode of land transport, other than railway, on behalf of postal and courier servicesThis subclass does not include:- messenger services of bicycle couriers, cf. 68021- courier delivery services, cf. 68021, 68022- local delivery services, cf. 68030

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65117. Road transport services of dry bulk
column5: Road transport services of dry bulk
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of dry bulk goods such as cereals, flours, cement, sand, coal, etc.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65118. Road transport services of live animals
column5: Road transport services of live animals
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of live animals

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65119. Other road transport services of freight
column5: Other road transport services of freight
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by road of other freight in other specialized vehicles not elsewhere classified, such as:* transport of concrete and tarred macadam* transport of cars- office equipment, machinery and furniture removal services- transportation by road of other freight not elsewhere classified, in non-specialized vehiclesThis subclass does not include:- armored car services, cf. 85240

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6512. Railway transport services of freight
column5: Railway transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65121. Railway transport services of freight by refrigerator cars
column5: Railway transport services of freight by refrigerator cars
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by railway of frozen or refrigerated goods, in specially refrigerated cars

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65122. Railway transport services of freight by tanker cars
column5: Railway transport services of freight by tanker cars
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by railway of petroleum products (crude oil, natural gas and refined petroleum products) in special tank cars- transportation by railway of other bulk liquids or gases in special tank cars

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65123. Railway transport services of intermodal containers
column5: Railway transport services of intermodal containers
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by railway of individual articles and packages assembled and shipped in specially constructed shipping containers designed for ease of handling in transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65124. Railway transport services of letters and parcels
column5: Railway transport services of letters and parcels
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation of letters and parcels by railway on behalf of postal and courier services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65125. Railway transport services of dry bulk goods
column5: Railway transport services of dry bulk goods
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by railway of dry bulk goods such as cereals, flours, cement, sand, coal etc.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65126. Railway transport services of live animals
column5: Railway transport services of live animals
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by railway of live animals

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65129. Other railway transport services of freight
column5: Other railway transport services of freight
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation by railway of cars, trucks and truck trailers- transportation by railway of other freight n.e.c.This subclass does not include:- transportation by railway of passengers and their accompanying vehicles, cf. 64210

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6513. Transport services via pipeline
column5: Transport services via pipeline

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65131. Transport services via pipeline of petroleum and natural gas
column5: Transport services via pipeline of petroleum and natural gas
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation via pipeline of crude or refined petroleum and petroleum products- transportation via pipeline of natural gasThis subclass does not include:- distribution services of natural gas through mains, cf. 69120, 86320- liquefaction and regasification services of natural gas, cf. 67990

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65139. Transport services via pipeline of other goods
column5: Transport services via pipeline of other goods
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation via pipeline of other chemical products, of coal slurry and of other products, not elsewhere classifiedThis subclass does not include:- distribution services of steam and of water through mains, cf. 69210, 69220, 86330, 86340

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 652. Water transport services of freight
column5: Water transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6521. Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of freight
column5: Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65211. Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of freight by refrigerator vessels
column5: Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of freight by refrigerator vessels
column6: This subclass includes:- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of frozen or refrigerated goods in specially refrigerated compartmentsThis subclass does not include:- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of liquid gas, cf. 65212

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65212. Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of freight by tankers
column5: Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of freight by tankers
column6: This subclass includes:- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of crude oil in special tankers- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of other bulk liquids or gases such as natural gas, methane and refined petroleum products in special tankers

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65213. Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of intermodal containers by container ships
column5: Coastal and transoceanic water transport services of intermodal containers by container ships
column6: This subclass includes:- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of individual articles and packages assembled and shipped in specially constructed shipping containers designed for ease of handling in transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65219. Other coastal and transoceanic water transport services of other freight
column5: Other coastal and transoceanic water transport services of other freight
column6: This subclass includes:- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of letters and parcels on behalf of postal and courier services- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of dry bulk goods such as cereals, flours, cement, sand, coal, etc.- towing and pushing services on the high seas and on coastal waters - towing services for oil rigs, floating cranes, dredging vessels and buoys, as well as ships' hulls and incomplete vessels, on coastal waters or the open sea- coastal and transoceanic water transportation of freight not elsewhere classified

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6522. Inland water transport services of freight
column5: Inland water transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65221. Inland water transport services of freight by refrigerator vessels
column5: Inland water transport services of freight by refrigerator vessels
column6: This subclass includes:- inland water transportation of frozen or refrigerated goods in specially refrigerated compartments

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65222. Inland water transport services of freight by tankers
column5: Inland water transport services of freight by tankers
column6: This subclass includes:- inland water transportation of crude oil in special tankers- inland water transportation of other bulk liquids or gases such as natural gas, methane and refined petroleum products in special tankers

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65229. Other inland water transport services of freight
column5: Other inland water transport services of freight
column6: This subclass includes:- inland water transportation of individual articles and packages assembled and shipped in specially constructed containers designed for ease of handling in transport- barge towing services on inland waterways and on canals, when provided by tugboats- towing services of oil rigs, floating cranes, dredging vessels and buoys, as well as ships' hulls and incomplete vessels, on inland waters- inland water transportation of freight not elsewhere classified

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 653. Air and space transport services of freight
column5: Air and space transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6531. Air transport services of freight
column5: Air transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65311. Air transport services of letters and parcels
column5: Air transport services of letters and parcels
column6: This subclass includes:- transportation of letters and parcels by air, scheduled or non-scheduled, on behalf of postal and courier services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65319. Air transport services of other freight
column5: Air transport services of other freight
column6: This subclass includes:- air transportation of individual articles and packages assembled and shipped in specially constructed shipping containers designed for ease of handling in transport- air transportation of freight not elsewhere classified

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6532. Space transport services of freight
column5: Space transport services of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 65320. Space transport services of freight
column5: Space transport services of freight
column6: This subclass includes:- space transportation of freight- launching and placing of satellites in space

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66. Rental services of transport vehicles with operators
column5: Rental services of transport vehicles with operators

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 660. Rental services of transport vehicles with operators
column5: Rental services of transport vehicles with operators

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6601. Rental services of road vehicles with operators
column5: Rental services of road vehicles with operators

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66011. Rental services of buses and coaches with operator
column5: Rental services of buses and coaches with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental of buses or coaches with operators for a period of time, not generally dependent on distance. The renter defines how and when the vehicles will be operated, determining schedules, routes, and other operational considerations.This subclass does not include:- local, urban and suburban bus or coach charter services, cf. 64118- long-distance bus or coach charter services, cf. 64223

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66012. Rental services of trucks with operator
column5: Rental services of trucks with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental of trucks and other motorized freight vehicles, with driverThis subclass does not include:- rental of trucks without driver, cf. 73112- road transportion of freight, cf. 6511

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6602. Rental services of water vessels with operator
column5: Rental services of water vessels with operator

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66021. Rental services of passenger vessels for coastal and transoceanic water transport with operator
column5: Rental services of passenger vessels for coastal and transoceanic water transport with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental services of all types of self-propelled passenger vessels for coastal and transoceanic water transport with crewThis subclass does not include:- rental and leasing services of vessels without crew, cf. 73115- rental and leasing services of pleasure boats without crew, cf. 73240

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66022. Rental services of freight vessels for coastal and transoceanic water transport with operator
column5: Rental services of freight vessels for coastal and transoceanic water transport with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental services of all types of self-propelled freight vessels for coastal and transoceanic water transport with crew, such as tankers, bulk dry cargo vessels, cargo and freight vessels, tugboats and fishing vesselsThis subclass does not include:- rental and leasing services of vessels without crew, cf. 73115

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66023. Rental services of passenger vessels for inland water transport with operator
column5: Rental services of passenger vessels for inland water transport with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental services of all types of self-propelled passenger vessels for inland water transport with crewThis subclass does not include:- rental and leasing of vessels without crew, cf. 73115- rental and leasing of inland water pleasure boats without crew, cf. 73240

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66024. Rental services of freight vessels for inland water transport with operator
column5: Rental services of freight vessels for inland water transport with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental services of all types of self-propelled freight vessels for inland water transport with crew, such as tankers, bulk dry cargo vessels, cargo and freight vessels, tugboats and fishing vesselsThis subclass does not include:- rental and leasing of vessels without crew, cf. 73115

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6603. Rental services of aircraft with operator
column5: Rental services of aircraft with operator

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66031. Rental services of passenger aircraft with operator
column5: Rental services of passenger aircraft with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental services of passenger aircraft or aircraft suitable for passenger and freight (including helicopters) with crewNote: These services are generally supplied on a time basis and several different destinations are frequently involved.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 66032. Rental services of freight aircraft with operator
column5: Rental services of freight aircraft with operator
column6: This subclass includes:- rental services of freight-carrying aircraft (including helicopters) with crewNote: These services are generally supplied on a time basis and several different destinations are frequently involved.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67. Supporting transport services
column5: Supporting transport services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 671. Cargo handling services
column5: Cargo handling services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6711. Container handling services
column5: Container handling services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67110. Container handling services
column5: Container handling services
column6: This subclass includes:- cargo handling services for containerized freight- services of container freight terminal facilities for all modes of transport, including stevedoring services (i.e. loading, unloading and discharging of vessels' containerized freight, at ports)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6719. Other cargo and baggage handling services
column5: Other cargo and baggage handling services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67190. Other cargo and baggage handling services
column5: Other cargo and baggage handling services
column6: This subclass includes:- cargo handling services for non-containerized freight- services of freight terminal facilities, for all modes of transport, including stevedoring services (i.e. loading, unloading and discharging of vessels' non-containerized freight, at ports)- cargo handling services incidental to freight transport not elsewhere classified- baggage handling services at airports and at bus, rail or highway vehicle terminals

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 672. Storage and warehousing services
column5: Storage and warehousing services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6721. Refrigerated storage services
column5: Refrigerated storage services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67210. Refrigerated storage services
column5: Refrigerated storage services
column6: This subclass includes:- storage and warehousing services for frozen or refrigerated goods, including perishable food products- blast freezing services, associated with storage and warehousingThis subclass does not include:- specialized freezing of food on a fee or contract basis, cf. corresponding subclass in group 881, based on type of good to be frozen

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6722. Bulk liquid or gas storage services
column5: Bulk liquid or gas storage services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67220. Bulk liquid or gas storage services
column5: Bulk liquid or gas storage services
column6: This subclass includes:- bulk storage and warehousing services for liquids and gases, including oil and oil products, wine and the like

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6729. Other storage and warehousing services
column5: Other storage and warehousing services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67290. Other storage and warehousing services
column5: Other storage and warehousing services
column6: This subclass includes:- storage services of grains- other storage or warehousing services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 673. Supporting services for railway transport
column5: Supporting services for railway transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67310. Railway pushing or towing services
column5: Railway pushing or towing services
column6: This subclass includes:- railway pushing or towing services, i.e. the movement of railway cars or wagons between terminal yards, industrial sidings and the like

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67390. Other supporting services for railway transport
column5: Other supporting services for railway transport
column6: This subclass includes:- railway passenger terminal services (sale of tickets, reservations, luggage office, left-luggage office)- other supporting services of railway transport, not elsewhere classifiedThis subclass does not include:- railway freight cargo handling services for containerized freight, cf. 67110- railway freight cargo handling services for non-containerized freight or passenger baggage, cf. 67190

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 674. Supporting services for road transport
column5: Supporting services for road transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6741. Bus station services
column5: Bus station services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67410. Bus station services
column5: Bus station services
column6: This subclass includes:- passenger terminal services in connection with urban, suburban and interurban bus passenger transport (sale of tickets, reservations, luggage office, left-luggage office)This subclass does not include:- baggage and freight handling services, cf. 67190

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6742. Highway, bridge and tunnel operation services
column5: Highway, bridge and tunnel operation services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67420. Highway, bridge and tunnel operation services
column5: Highway, bridge and tunnel operation services
column6: This subclass includes:- operation services of highways, roads, streets and causeways- operation services of bridges and tunnelThis subclass does not include:- services of vehicle parking facilities, cf. 67430

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6743. Parking lot services
column5: Parking lot services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67430. Parking lot services
column5: Parking lot services
column6: This subclass includes:- provision of parking spaces for motor vehicles, motorcycles and bicycles provided in roofed or unroofed car parks, parking lots and parking garages, whether or not roofed- collection of fees for parking on streets, roads and public placesThis subclass does not include:- rental of vehicle parking spaces in lock-up garages or garage premises, by the month or year, cf. 72112- car parking services, cf. 97990

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6744. Towing services for commercial and private vehicles
column5: Towing services for commercial and private vehicles

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67440. Towing services for commercial and private vehicles
column5: Towing services for commercial and private vehicles
column6: This subclass includes:- towing services for distressed commercial and private vehicles- towing services for other vehicles, e.g., for parking violations

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6749. Other supporting services for road transport
column5: Other supporting services for road transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67490. Other supporting services for road transport
column5: Other supporting services for road transport
column6: This subclass includes:- other supporting services for road transport n.e.c.This subclass does not include:- cleaning services for buses and other land transport vehicles, cf. 85340

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 675. Supporting services for water transport
column5: Supporting services for water transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6751. Port and waterway operation services (excl. cargo handling)
column5: Port and waterway operation services (excl. cargo handling)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67511. Port and waterway operation services (excl. cargo handling), on coastal and transoceanic waters
column5: Port and waterway operation services (excl. cargo handling), on coastal and transoceanic waters
column6: This subclass includes:- operation services of ports, such as wharves, docks, piers or quays and other services connected with coastal and transoceanic marine terminal facilities, including passenger terminals- services to coastal and transoceanic shipping, provided by locks, boat lifts, weirs, sluices- services to coastal and transoceanic shipping, provided by lighthouses, lightships and light vessels, buoys, channel markers and similar aids to navigationThis subclass does not include:- stevedoring services:* for containerized freight, cf. 67110* for non-containerized freight, cf. 67190- port storage and warehousing services, cf. 672- pilotage services in connection with docking and undocking of vessels, on coastal and transoceanic waters, cf. 67521- tugboat-assisted docking and undocking services on coastal and transoceanic waters, cf. 67521

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67512. Inland waterway operation services (excl. cargo handling)
column5: Inland waterway operation services (excl. cargo handling)
column6: This subclass includes:- operating and maintenance services of boat, barge and ship canals, of canalized rivers and of other artificial or non artificial inland waterways- services of locks, boat lifts, weirs, sluices- towing of inland water vessels on canals other than by tugboat, e.g., by tractors or locomotives on the tow-path- services to inland shipping provided by lightships and light vessels, buoys, channel markers and similar aids to navigationThis subclass does not include:- stevedoring services:* for containerized freight, cf. 67110* for non-containerized freight, cf. 67190- port storage and warehousing services, cf. 672- pilotage services in connection with docking and undocking of vessels, on inland waters, cf. 67522- tugboat-assisted docking and undocking services, on inland waters, cf. 67522

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6752. Pilotage and berthing services
column5: Pilotage and berthing services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67521. Pilotage and berthing services on coastal and transoceanic waters
column5: Pilotage and berthing services on coastal and transoceanic waters
column6: This subclass includes:- pilotage services, including the services of pilot vessels, on coastal and transoceanic waters, whether supplied to conduct a vessel in or out of harbours or around navigational dangers- tugboat services in connection with the docking and undocking of vessels of all types, on coastal and transoceanic watersThis subclass does not include:- towing and pushing services on coastal waters or on open sea, cf. 65219

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67522. Pilotage and berthing services in inland waters
column5: Pilotage and berthing services in inland waters
column6: This subclass includes:- pilotage services, including the services of pilot vessels, whether supplied to conduct a vessel in or out of harbours or around navigational dangers, in inland waters- tugboat services in connection with the docking and undocking of vessels of all types, in inland watersThis subclass does not include:- towing and pushing services on inland waters, cf. 65229

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6753. Vessel salvage and refloating services
column5: Vessel salvage and refloating services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67531. Vessel salvage and refloating services on coastal and transoceanic waters
column5: Vessel salvage and refloating services on coastal and transoceanic waters
column6: This subclass includes:- vessel salvage services, provided on coastal and transoceanic waters, i.e. services consisting of recovering distressed and sunken vessels and their cargoes, including the raising of sunken vessels, the righting of capsized vessels and the refloating of stranded vessels- towing services for distressed vessels on coastal and transoceanic watersThis subclass does not include:- towing services provided to distressed vessels on coastal waters or on the open sea, cf. 65219- lifeboat services, marine fireboat services and other marine search and rescue services:* police services, cf. 91260* marine fireboat services, cf. 91260* other public order- and safety affairs- related services, cf. 91290

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67532. Vessel salvage and refloating services in inland waters
column5: Vessel salvage and refloating services in inland waters
column6: This subclass includes:- vessel salvage services, provided on inland waters, i.e. services consisting of recovering distressed and sunken vessels and their cargoes, including the raising of sunken vessels, the righting of capsized vessels and the refloating of stranded vessels- towing services for distressed vessels on inland watersThis subclass does not include:- towing services provided to distressed vessels on inland waters, cf. 65229- lifeboat services, marine fireboat services and other marine search and rescue services:* police services, cf. 91260* marine fireboat services, cf. 91260* other public order- and safety affairs-related services, cf. 91290

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6759. Other supporting services for water transport
column5: Other supporting services for water transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67590. Other supporting services for water transport
column5: Other supporting services for water transport
column6: This subclass includes:- water transport supporting services directly connected with vessel operations not elsewhere classified, and not directly connected with vessel operations such as ice breaking, vessel registration, vessel laying-up and storage services, etc.This subclass does not include:- cleaning services for vessels, including removal of contamination by fuel and oil, cf. 853- disinfecting and exterminating services for vessels, cf. 85310- lifeboat services, marine fireboat services and other marine search and rescue services:* police services, cf. 91260* marine fireboat services, cf. 91260* other public order and safety affairs related services, cf. 91290* oil spill fighting services, cf. 94412, 94420

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 676. Supporting services for air or space transport
column5: Supporting services for air or space transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6761. Airport operation services (excl. cargo handling)
column5: Airport operation services (excl. cargo handling)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67610. Airport operation services (excl. cargo handling)
column5: Airport operation services (excl. cargo handling)
column6: This subclass includes:- passenger air terminal services and ground services on air fields, including runway operating servicesThis subclass does not include:- air terminal cargo-handling services:* for containerized freight, cf. 67110* for non-containerized freight or for passenger baggage, cf. 67190- runway cleaning and snow removal services, cf. 94510

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6762. Air traffic control services
column5: Air traffic control services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67620. Air traffic control services
column5: Air traffic control services
column6: This subclass includes:- flight control tower operation services, including approach, landing and take-off control services- services provided by airport-located radar stationsThis subclass does not include:- radio navigational aid services, cf. 67990

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6763. Other supporting services for air transport
column5: Other supporting services for air transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67630. Other supporting services for air transport
column5: Other supporting services for air transport
column6: This subclass includes:- other supporting services for air transport, such as:* aircraft firefighting and fire prevention services* aircraft maintenance and upkeep services (excluding repairs)* hangar services* aircraft towingThis subclass does not include:- disinfecting and exterminating services for aircraft, cf. 85310- cleaning services for aircraft, cf. 85340- air-sea rescue services, cf. 91260- general flying school services, cf. 92919- runway cleaning and snow removal services, cf. 94510

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6764. Supporting services for space transport
column5: Supporting services for space transport

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67640. Supporting services for space transport
column5: Supporting services for space transport
column6: This subclass includes:- specialized support services for space transportation

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 679. Other supporting transport services
column5: Other supporting transport services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6791. Freight transport agency services and other freight transport services
column5: Freight transport agency services and other freight transport services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67910. Freight transport agency services and other freight transport services
column5: Freight transport agency services and other freight transport services
column6: This subclass includes:- ship-broker services- freight brokerage services- freight forwarding services (primarily transport organization or arrangement services on behalf of the shipper or consignee)- aircraft space brokerage services- freight consolidation and break-bulk services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6799. Other supporting transport services n.e.c.
column5: Other supporting transport services n.e.c.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 67990. Other supporting transport services n.e.c.
column5: Other supporting transport services n.e.c.
column6: This subclass includes:- type rating services (aircraft-specific permits for flying a particular type of plane)- liquefaction and regasification of natural gas for transportation- radio navigational aid locating services, such as GPS (global positioning system) provision

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68. Postal and courier services
column5: Postal and courier services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 680. Postal and courier services
column5: Postal and courier services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6801. Postal services
column5: Postal services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68011. Postal services related to letters
column5: Postal services related to letters
column6: This subclass includes:- collection, transport and delivery services for newspapers, journals and periodicals, whether for domestic or foreign destinations, rendered under a universal service obligation- collection, transport and delivery services for letters, brochures, leaflets and similar printed matter, whether for domestic or foreign destinations, rendered under a universal service obligation

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68012. Postal services related to parcels
column5: Postal services related to parcels
column6: This subclass includes:- collection, transport and delivery services for parcels and packages, whether for domestic or foreign destinations, rendered under a universal service obligation

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68013. Post office counter services
column5: Post office counter services
column6: This subclass includes:- sales of postage stamps, handling of certified or registered letters and packets, and other post office counter services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68019. Other postal services
column5: Other postal services
column6: This subclass includes:- mailbox rental, "poste restante" and other public postal services not elsewhere classifiedThis subclass does not include:- services related to postal giro and postal savings accounts, cf. 71- telecommunications services, cf. 84

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6802. Courier services
column5: Courier services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68021. Domestic courier services
column5: Domestic courier services
column6: This subclass includes:- collection, transport and delivery services for domestic destinations of letters, parcels, and packages, as rendered by courier and using one or more modes of transport, other than those rendered under a universal service obligation- messenger services provided by bicycle couriersThis subclass does not include:- collection, transport and delivery of letters, parcels and packages for international destinations, cf. 68022- collection, transport and delivery of letters, rendered under a universal service obligation, cf. 68011- collection, transport and delivery of parcels and packages, rendered under a universal service obligation, cf. 68012- local freight delivery services, cf. 68030

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68022. International courier services
column5: International courier services
column6: This subclass includes:- collection, transport and delivery services for international destinations of letters, parcels, and packages, as rendered by courier using one or more modes of transport, other than those rendered under a universal service obligationThis subclass does not include:- collection, transport and delivery of letters, parcels and packages for domestic destinations, cf. 68021- collection, transport and delivery of letters, rendered under a universal service obligation, cf. 68011- collection, transport and delivery of parcels and packages, rendered under a universal service obligation, cf. 68012

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6803. Local delivery services
column5: Local delivery services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 68030. Local delivery services
column5: Local delivery services
column6: This subclass includes:- local delivery services of items such as food and other purchasesThis subclass does not include:- moving services of household furniture and goods, cf. 65115- moving services of office furniture and other goods, cf. 65119- courier and messenger services by bicycle, cf. 68021

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69. Electricity, gas and water distribution (on own account)
column5: Electricity, gas and water distribution (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 691. Electricity and gas distribution (on own account)
column5: Electricity and gas distribution (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6911. Electricity transmission and distribution (on own account)
column5: Electricity transmission and distribution (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69111. Transmission of electricity (on own account)
column5: Transmission of electricity (on own account)
column6: This subclass includes:- own-account transmission of electricityThis subclass does not include:- installation of electric meters, cf. 54611- distribution of electricity, cf. 69112, 86312- electricity transmission services (on a fee or contract basis), cf. 86311

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69112. Distribution of electricity (on own account)
column5: Distribution of electricity (on own account)
column6: This subclass includes:- own-account distribution of electricity- maintenance of electric metersThis subclass does not include:- installation of electric meters, cf. 54611- transmission of electricity, cf. 69111, 86311- reading of electric meters, cf. 85999- electricity distribution services (on a fee or contract basis), cf. 86312

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6912. Gas distribution through mains (on own account)
column5: Gas distribution through mains (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69120. Gas distribution through mains (on own account)
column5: Gas distribution through mains (on own account)
column6: This subclass includes:- own-account distribution of gaseous fuels through mains- maintenance of gas metersThis subclass does not include:- installation services of gas meters, cf. 54611- transportation services of gases by pipelines, cf. 65131- gas distribution services through mains (on a fee or contract basis), cf. 86320- reading of gas meters, cf. 85999

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 692. Water distribution (on own account)
column5: Water distribution (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6921. Water distribution through mains, except steam and hot water (on own account)
column5: Water distribution through mains, except steam and hot water (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69210. Water distribution through mains, except steam and hot water (on own account)
column5: Water distribution through mains, except steam and hot water (on own account)
column6: This subclass includes:- own-account distribution of water through mains- maintenance of water metersThis subclass does not include:- installation of water meters, cf. 54611- reading of water meters, cf. 85999- operation of irrigation systems for agricultural purposes, cf. 86119- water distribution services through mains (on a fee or contract basis), cf. 86330

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6922. Distribution of steam, hot water and air-conditioning supply through mains (on own account)
column5: Distribution of steam, hot water and air-conditioning supply through mains (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69220. Distribution of steam, hot water and air-conditioning supply through mains (on own account)
column5: Distribution of steam, hot water and air-conditioning supply through mains (on own account)
column6: This subclass includes:- own-account distribution of steam and hot water for heating, power and other purposes- own-account distribution of cooled air- own-account distribution of chilled water for cooling purposesThis subclass does not include:- steam and hot water distribution services through mains (on a fee or contract basis), cf. 86340

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 6923. Water distribution, except through mains (on own account)
column5: Water distribution, except through mains (on own account)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 69230. Water distribution, except through mains (on own account)
column5: Water distribution, except through mains (on own account)
column6: This subclass includes:- own-account distribution of water by trucks and other meansThis subclass does not include:- operation of irrigation systems for agricultural purposes, cf. 86119- water distribution services, except through mains (on a fee or contract basis), cf. 86350

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7. Financial and related services; real estate services; and rental and leasing services
column5: Financial and related services; real estate services; and rental and leasing services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71. Financial and related services
column5: Financial and related services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 711. Financial services, except investment banking, insurance services and pension services
column5: Financial services, except investment banking, insurance services and pension services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7111. Central banking services
column5: Central banking services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71110. Central banking services
column5: Central banking services
column6: This subclass includes:- services which support the country's systems for clearing and settling payments and other financial transactions - services of maintaining deposit accounts for major financial institutions and for the central government - services of implementing monetary policy- services of managing the government's foreign exchange reserves- services of influencing the value of currency- currency services under the authority of the central bank, including currency design and production, issuing, distribution and replacement- fiscal agency services including advisory services to the government on matters relating to the public debt, issuing debt instruments, maintaining bondholder records and making interest and redemption payments on behalf of the government- supervisory activities with regard to banks and/or non-banks if undertaken by the central bank- other central banking services n.e.c.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7112. Deposit services
column5: Deposit services
column6: This class includes:- demand, notice and term deposit services provided to depositors- administration of bank accounts- chequing services:* certification of cheques* exchanging cheques or withdrawal slips for money* remitting cheques forwarded for collection- transferring money between accounts- providing documents to clients

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71121. Deposit services to corporate and institutional depositors
column5: Deposit services to corporate and institutional depositors
column6: This subclass includes:- provision of services listed in class 7112 to large business and institutional customers, including governmentsThis subclass does not include:- wrapping, rolling or otherwise handling currency and coin on behalf of customers cf. 85400- collection services of drafts, cheques and other bills of exchange received on a collection basis cashed or taken on deposit cf. 85920- collection services of accounts or monies receivable under assignment of accounts or contracts, cf. 85920

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71122. Deposit services to other depositors
column5: Deposit services to other depositors
column6: This subclass includes:- provision of services listed in class 7112 to depositors, other than corporate and institutional depositorsThis subclass does not include:- wrapping, rolling or otherwise handling currency and coin on behalf of customers cf. 85400- collection services of drafts, cheques and other bills of exchange received on a collection basis cashed or taken on deposit cf. 85920- collection services of accounts or monies receivable under assignment of accounts or contracts, cf. 85920

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7113. Credit-granting services
column5: Credit-granting services
column6: This class includes:- issuing and physical management of loansNote: These services may be provided by a number of different types of lenders, including, for example, banks and insurance companies.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71131. Residential mortgage loan services
column5: Residential mortgage loan services
column6: This subclass includes:- granting of loans for the purpose of acquiring residential land or buildings and for which the land or buildings are used as security- home equity loansThis subclass does not include:- real estate appraisal services, cf. 72240

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71132. Non-residential mortgage loan services
column5: Non-residential mortgage loan services
column6: This subclass includes:- granting of loans for the purpose of acquiring non-residential land or buildings and for which the land or buildings are used as security This subclass does not include:- real estate appraisal services, cf. 72240

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71133. Personal non-mortgage loan services for non-business purposes
column5: Personal non-mortgage loan services for non-business purposes
column6: This subclass includes:- granting of personal non-mortgage installment loans with scheduled repayment plans- line-of-credit loan services, that is, loan services based on a commitment to lend funds to a borrower up to a specified amount- consumer loan services, that is, loan services extended for financing consumer purchases of goods or services where the purchased good is generally used as collateral

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71134. Credit card loan services
column5: Credit card loan services
column6: This subclass includes:- granting credit when the holder of a credit card uses it to buy a good or a service, regardless of whether the balance is paid in full at the end of the grace period

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71135. Non-mortgage loan services for business purposes
column5: Non-mortgage loan services for business purposes
column6: This subclass includes:- granting loans to investment dealers and brokers, regulated financial institutions, federal, regional and local governments or non-profit institutions, foreign governments, and other businesses - granting loans to individuals for business purposes- standby, commitment and other loan services including overdraft services- providing letters of credit- acceptance services, that is, agreements by a bank or other financial institution to pay a draft or a credit instrument issued by an institution

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71139. Other credit-granting services
column5: Other credit-granting services
column6: This subclass includes:- sales financing services- other credit-granting services n.e.c.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7114. Financial leasing services
column5: Financial leasing services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71140. Financial leasing services
column5: Financial leasing services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of making equipment and other assets available to a customer without capital investment on the customer's part, whereby the lessor pays for and takes title to the equipment or facilities and leases it to the lessee while retaining few of the normal responsibilities of ownership This subclass does not include:- operating leasing services, cf. 73

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7119. Other financial services, except investment banking, insurance services and pension services
column5: Other financial services, except investment banking, insurance services and pension services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71190. Other financial services, except investment banking, insurance services and pension services
column5: Other financial services, except investment banking, insurance services and pension services
column6: This subclass includes:- factoring services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 712. Investment banking services
column5: Investment banking services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7120. Investment banking services
column5: Investment banking services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71200. Investment banking services
column5: Investment banking services
column6: This subclass includes:- securities underwriting services- guaranteeing the sale of an issue of securities at a stated price from the issuing corporation or government and reselling it to investors- engaging to sell as much of an issue of securities as possible without making a guarantee to purchase the entire offering from the issuer

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 713. Insurance and pension services (excluding reinsurance services), except compulsory social security services
column5: Insurance and pension services (excluding reinsurance services), except compulsory social security services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7131. Life insurance and pension services (excluding reinsurance services)
column5: Life insurance and pension services (excluding reinsurance services)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71311. Life insurance services
column5: Life insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide for the payment of claims to beneficiaries contingent upon the death of the insured individual or upon the maturation of the policy. Policies may provide pure protection or may also contain a savings component. Policies may cover individuals or members of groups.This subclass does not include:- accidental death insurance services, cf. 71321

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71312. Individual pension services
column5: Individual pension services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of annuities, i.e. plans which provide income payments at regular intervals to individuals. Plans may require a single contribution or a series of contributions; may be compulsory or optional; may have nominal benefits determined in advance or dependent on the market value of aspects supporting the plan; and, if related to employment, may or may not be portable with a change in employment. The duration of the period during which benefits are paid may be fixed in terms of a minimum or maximum; there may or may not be survivors' benefits.This subclass does not include:- portfolio management services (except pension funds), cf. 71530- trust services, cf. 71541- pension fund management services, cf. 71640- pension fund administration, cf. 71690

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71313. Group pension services
column5: Group pension services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of plans which provide income payments at regular intervals to members of groups. Plans may require a single contribution or a series of contributions; may be compulsory or optional; may have nominal benefits determined in advance or dependent on the market value of assets supporting the plan; and, if related to employment, may or may not be portable with a change in employment. The duration of the period during which benefits are paid may be fixed in terms of a minimum or maximum; there may or may not be survivors' benefits.This subclass does not include:- portfolio management services (except pension funds), cf. 71530- trust services, cf. 71541- pension fund management services, cf. 71640- pension fund administration, cf. 71690

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7132. Accident and health insurance services
column5: Accident and health insurance services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71321. Accidental death and dismemberment insurance services
column5: Accidental death and dismemberment insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide accidental death and dismemberment insurance, that is, payment in the event than an accident results in death or loss of one or more bodily members (such as hands or feet) or the sight of one or both eyesThis subclass does not include:- life insurance services, cf. 71311- travel insurance services, cf. 71337

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71322. Health insurance services
column5: Health insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide protection for hospital and medical expenses not covered by government programmes and, usually, other health-care expenses such as prescribed drugs, medical appliances, ambulance, private duty nursing, etc.- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide protection for dental expenses- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide periodic payments when the insured is unable to work as a result of a disability due to illness or injuryThis subclass does not include:- travel insurance services, cf. 71337

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7133. Other non-life insurance services (excluding reinsurance services)
column5: Other non-life insurance services (excluding reinsurance services)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71331. Motor vehicle insurance services
column5: Motor vehicle insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks relating to the use of motor vehicles, including those used to transport paying passengers. Risks covered include liability and loss of or damage to the vehicle.- freight motor vehicle insurance services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71332. Marine, aviation, and other transport insurance services
column5: Marine, aviation, and other transport insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks relating to the use of:* commercial passenger and freight vessels, whether operating on oceans, coastal waterways or inland waterways* commercial aircraft* railway rolling stock- satellite launching insurance servicesNote: Risks covered include liability, hull damage or loss of the vessel, and loss of or damage to aircraft or railway rolling stockThis subclass does not include:- underwriting services of insurance policies for non-commercial vessels and aircraft, cf. 71334

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71333. Freight insurance services
column5: Freight insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide coverage, additional to that provided by transport companies, for risks of damage to or loss of freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71334. Other property insurance services
column5: Other property insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks of damage to or loss of property excluding that covered in subclass 71331 (Motor vehicle insurance services), 71332 (Marine, aviation, and other transport insurance services) and 71333 (Freight insurance services). Risks covered may include fire, theft, explosion, storm, hail, frost, natural forces, radioactive contamination and land subsidence- underwriting services of insurance policies for non-commercial vessels and aircraft- underwriting services of insurance policies for boilers and machinery, which covers property spoilage from lack of power, light, heat, steam or refrigeration

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71335. General liability insurance services
column5: General liability insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks of all types of liability including liability for defective products, bodily injury, property damage, pollution, malpractice, etc., other than liability covered in subclass 71331 (Motor vehicle insurance services), 71332 (Marine, aviation and other transport insurance services) and 71334 (Other property insurance services)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71336. Credit and surety insurance services
column5: Credit and surety insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks of excessive credit losses because of debtor insolvency- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks of non-performance or failure to satisfy a contractual financial obligation by a party to a contract or agreement

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71337. Travel insurance services
column5: Travel insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of insurance policies which provide protection for travel related expenses (typically provided in a package), such as:* trip cancellation, interruption or delay* lost, delayed or damaged luggage* accident and health medical expenses* repatriation of remainsThis subclass does not include:- motor vehicle insurance, cf. 71331

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71339. Other non-life insurance services
column5: Other non-life insurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- underwriting services of policies for legal expense insurance, mortgage insurance, fidelity insurance or title insurance- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover risks of miscellaneous financial loss, that is, expenses arising from the following risks: loss of employment, insufficiency of income (general), bad weather, loss of benefits, continuing general expenses, unforeseen trading expenses, loss of market value, loss of rent or revenue, indirect trading losses (other than those mentioned above), other financial loss (non-trading) and other forms of loss- underwriting services of insurance policies which cover other non-life risks n.e.c.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 714. Reinsurance services
column5: Reinsurance services
column6: This group includes:- services of assuming all or part of insurance policies originally underwritten by other insurance carriers

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7141. Life reinsurance services
column5: Life reinsurance services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71410. Life reinsurance services
column5: Life reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- reinsurance services for life insurance- reinsurance of annuities

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7142. Accident and health reinsurance services
column5: Accident and health reinsurance services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71420. Accident and health reinsurance services
column5: Accident and health reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- reinsurance services for accident and health insurance- reinsurance of annuities

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7143. Other non-life reinsurance services
column5: Other non-life reinsurance services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71431. Motor vehicle reinsurance services
column5: Motor vehicle reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- reinsurance services for motor vehicle insurance policies

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71432. Marine, aviation and other transport reinsurance services
column5: Marine, aviation and other transport reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- reinsurance services for marine, aviation and other transport insurance policies

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71433. Freight reinsurance services
column5: Freight reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- reinsurance services for freight insurance policies

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71434. Other property reinsurance services
column5: Other property reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- property reinsurance services, other than for motor vehicles and freight

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71435. General liability reinsurance services
column5: General liability reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- liability reinsurance services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71436. Credit and surety reinsurance services
column5: Credit and surety reinsurance services
column6: This subclass includes:- reinsurance services for surety bonds

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71439. Other non-life reinsurance services, n.e.c.
column5: Other non-life reinsurance services, n.e.c.
column6: This subclass includes:- non-life reinsurance services, not elsewhere specified

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 715. Services auxiliary to financial services other than to insurance and pensions
column5: Services auxiliary to financial services other than to insurance and pensions

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7151. Services related to investment banking
column5: Services related to investment banking

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71511. Mergers and acquisition services
column5: Mergers and acquisition services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of counsellors and negotiators in arranging mergers and acquisitions

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71512. Corporate finance and venture capital services
column5: Corporate finance and venture capital services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of arranging corporate financing, including:* debt financing* equity financing* venture capital financing

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71519. Other services related to investment banking
column5: Other services related to investment banking
column6: This subclass includes:- other services related to investment banking n.e.c.This subclass does not include:- portfolio management services, cf. 71530- trust and custody services, cf. 7154- stock price quotation services made available through an information server, cf. 84399- supply of financial news to the news media, cf. 844

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7152. Brokerage and related securities and commodities services
column5: Brokerage and related securities and commodities services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71521. Securities brokerage services
column5: Securities brokerage services
column6: This subclass includes:- brokerage services (that is bringing together purchasers and sellers of the same instrument) for securities- services of acting as a selling agent of units, shares or other interests in a mutual (investment) fund- sales, delivery and redemption services of government bonds- brokerage of optionsThis subclass does not include:- brokerage of commodities, cf. 71522

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71522. Commodity brokerage services
column5: Commodity brokerage services
column6: This subclass includes:- brokerage services for commodities and commodity futures, including financial futures- brokerage services for financial derivatives, other than optionsThis subclass does not include:- brokerage of options, cf. 71521

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71523. Processing and clearing services of securities transactions
column5: Processing and clearing services of securities transactions
column6: This subclass includes:- computer-based clearing and settlement for interchange of debits, credits and transfer of ownership of securities

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7153. Portfolio management services except pension funds
column5: Portfolio management services except pension funds

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71530. Portfolio management services except pension funds
column5: Portfolio management services except pension funds
column6: This subclass includes:- managing portfolio assets of others, on a fee or commission basis, except for pension fundsNote: Managers make decisions on which investments to purchase or sell. Examples of the portfolios managed are the portfolios of mutual and other investment funds or trustsThis subclass does not include:- management of pension funds, cf. 71640- personal financial planning advisory services not involving decision-making on behalf of clients, cf. 71591- buying and selling of securities on a transaction fee basis, cf. 71521

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7154. Trust and custody services
column5: Trust and custody services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71541. Trust services
column5: Trust services
column6: This subclass includes:- estate and trust management and administration services- services of acting as a trustee of investment funds or pension funds- services of acting as trustee for securities (administrative services related to the issue and registration of securities, and payment of interest and dividends)

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71542. Custody services
column5: Custody services
column6: This subclass includes:- provision, under instructions, of safekeeping of and accounting for valuable and usually income-bearing personal property, including securities- safekeeping services- safe deposit services- security custody services- audit confirmation services with respect to customers' securities held for safekeeping

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7155. Services related to the administration of financial markets
column5: Services related to the administration of financial markets

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71551. Financial market operational services
column5: Financial market operational services
column6: This subclass includes:- administrative services of furnishing space and other facilities necessary for the operation of security and commodity exchanges

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71552. Financial market regulatory services
column5: Financial market regulatory services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of regulating and monitoring financial markets and participants in those markets

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71559. Other financial market administration services
column5: Other financial market administration services
column6: This subclass includes:- other financial market administration services n.e.c.This subclass does not include:- security custody services, cf. 71542- stock price quotation services made available through an information server, cf. 84399- supply of financial news to the news media, cf. 844

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7159. Other services auxiliary to financial services
column5: Other services auxiliary to financial services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71591. Financial consultancy services
column5: Financial consultancy services
column6: This subclass includes:- financial advisory services- market analysis and intelligenceThis subclass does not include:- insurance and pension consultancy services, cf. 71690- mergers and acquisitions services, cf. 71511- corporate finance and venture capital services, cf. 71512- portfolio management services (except pension funds), cf. 71530- trust and custody services, cf. 7154- pension fund management services, cf. 71640- advisory services on taxation matters, cf. 823- financial management consulting services (except business tax), cf. 83112

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71592. Foreign exchange services
column5: Foreign exchange services
column6: This subclass includes:- foreign currency exchange services provided by bureaux de change, etc.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71593. Financial transactions processing and clearinghouse services
column5: Financial transactions processing and clearinghouse services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of processing financial transactions such as verification of financial balances, authorization of transactions, transfer of funds to and from transactors' accounts, notification of banks (or credit card issuers) of individual transactions and provision of daily summaries- services of clearing cheques, drafts and other payment orders- debit card and credit card merchant servicesThis subclass does not include:- services of processing securities transactions, cf. 71523

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71599. Other services auxiliary to financial services n.e.c.
column5: Other services auxiliary to financial services n.e.c.
column6: This subclass includes:- mortgage and loan brokerage servicesThis subclass does not include:- coin and currency packing services, cf. 85400

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 716. Services auxiliary to insurance and pensions
column5: Services auxiliary to insurance and pensions

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7161. Insurance brokerage and agency services
column5: Insurance brokerage and agency services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71610. Insurance brokerage and agency services
column5: Insurance brokerage and agency services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of selling insurance and pension products

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7162. Insurance claims adjustment services
column5: Insurance claims adjustment services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71620. Insurance claims adjustment services
column5: Insurance claims adjustment services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of investigating insurance claims, determining the amount of loss or damages covered by insurance policies and negotiating settlements- services of examining claims which have been investigated and authorization of payments- damage assessment services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7163. Actuarial services
column5: Actuarial services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71630. Actuarial services
column5: Actuarial services
column6: This subclass includes:- services of calculating insurance risks and premiums

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7164. Pension fund management services
column5: Pension fund management services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71640. Pension fund management services
column5: Pension fund management services
column6: This subclass includes:- pension fund management services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7169. Other services auxiliary to insurance and pensions
column5: Other services auxiliary to insurance and pensions

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71690. Other services auxiliary to insurance and pensions
column5: Other services auxiliary to insurance and pensions
column6: This subclass includes:- administration of insurance and pension funds- salvage administration services- insurance and pension consultancy services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 717. Services of holding financial assets
column5: Services of holding financial assets

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7170. Services of holding financial assets
column5: Services of holding financial assets

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71701. Services of holding equity of subsidiary companies
column5: Services of holding equity of subsidiary companies
column6: This subclass includes:- services provided by holding companies, i.e. holding securities of (or other equity interests in) companies and enterprises for the purpose of owning a controlling interest

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 71702. Services of holding securities and other assets of trusts and funds and similar financial entities
column5: Services of holding securities and other assets of trusts and funds and similar financial entities
column6: This subclass includes:- services provided by legal entities that are organized to pool securities or other financial assets, without managing, on behalf of shareholders or beneficiaries

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72. Real estate services
column5: Real estate services

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 721. Real estate services involving own or leased property
column5: Real estate services involving own or leased property

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7211. Rental or leasing services involving own or leased property
column5: Rental or leasing services involving own or leased property

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72111. Rental or leasing services involving own or leased residential property
column5: Rental or leasing services involving own or leased residential property
column6: This subclass includes:- rental or leasing services concerning residential properties by owners or leaseholders:* houses, flats, apartment buildings* multiple-use buildings that are primarily residential* residential mobile home sitesThis subclass does not include:- accommodation services provided by operating hotels, motels, rooming houses, school dormitories, camp sites and other lodging places, cf. 631

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72112. Rental or leasing services involving own or leased non-residential property
column5: Rental or leasing services involving own or leased non-residential property
column6: This subclass includes:- rental or leasing services concerning industrial, commercial or other non-residential buildings or property by owners or leaseholders, such as:* factories, office buildings, warehouses* theatres, convention centres, exhibition halls and multiple-use buildings that are primarily non-residential* agricultural, forestry and similar properties- rental or leasing of caravan sites, lock-up garages or other places for parking vehicles, by the month or year

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7212. Trade services of buildings
column5: Trade services of buildings

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72121. Trade services of residential buildings
column5: Trade services of residential buildings
column6: This subclass includes:- sales on own account of residential buildings and associated land in cases where the sales are treated as sales of trading stock by the seller, but not sales of property where the sales are disposals of the fixed assets of the selling unit- sales of houses with associated land, multiple-dwelling buildings with associated land and individual dwelling units within such buildings, such as individual apartments or condominiums. Such property can be either leasehold or freehold.This subclass does not include:- sales of vacant land, cf. 72130

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72122. Trade services of non-residential buildings
column5: Trade services of non-residential buildings
column6: This subclass includes:- sales on own account of non-residential buildings and associated land in cases where the sales are treated as sales of trading stock by the seller, but not sales of property where the sales are disposals of the fixed assets of the selling unit. Examples of non-residential properties include:* factories, office buildings, warehouses* theatres, multiple-use buildings that are primarily non-residential* hotels* agriculture, forestry properties* similar propertiesNote: Such property can either be leasehold or freeholdThis subclass does not include:- sales of vacant land, cf. 72130

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72123. Trade services of time-share properties
column5: Trade services of time-share properties
column6: This subclass includes:- sale on own account of time-share properties

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7213. Trade services of vacant and subdivided land
column5: Trade services of vacant and subdivided land

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72130. Trade services of vacant and subdivided land
column5: Trade services of vacant and subdivided land
column6: This subclass includes:- sales on own account of vacant residential or non-residential land in cases where the sales are treated as sales of trading stock by the seller. Such vacant land can include subdivided vacant land.

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 722. Real estate services on a fee or contract basis
column5: Real estate services on a fee or contract basis

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7221. Property management services on a fee or contract basis
column5: Property management services on a fee or contract basis

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72211. Residential property management services on a fee or contract basis except of time-share ownership properties
column5: Residential property management services on a fee or contract basis except of time-share ownership properties
column6: This subclass includes:- management services concerning houses and other residential properties, on a fee or contract basis- management services concerning multi-apartment apartment buildings (or multiple-use buildings that are primarily residential)- management services concerning residential mobile home sites- management services concerning dwellings in joint ownership- rent collection servicesThis subclass does not include:- time-share (ownership type) property management services on a fee or contract basis, cf. 72213

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72212. Non-residential property management services on a fee or contract basis
column5: Non-residential property management services on a fee or contract basis
column6: This subclass includes:- management services concerning industrial and commercial properties, multiple-use buildings that are primarily non-residential, etc.- management services concerning agricultural, forestry and similar propertiesThis subclass does not include:- sports and recreational sports facility operation services, cf. 96520- operation of other recreation and amusement service facilities n.e.c., cf. 96990

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72213. Time-share property management services on a fee or contract basis
column5: Time-share property management services on a fee or contract basis
column6: This subclass includes:- management services concerning buildings or properties used on a time-share basis

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 7222. Building sales on a fee or contract basis
column5: Building sales on a fee or contract basis

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72221. Residential building sales on a fee or contract basis, except of time-share ownership properties
column5: Residential building sales on a fee or contract basis, except of time-share ownership properties
column6: This subclass includes:- real estate agency and brokerage services related to the sale of houses, flats, apartment buildings and other residential properties, and similar intermediation services involving buying, selling and renting of residential buildings and associated land land, on a fee or contract basisThis subclass does not include:- sale of time-share properties on a fee or contract basis, cf. 72223- sale of land on a fee or contract basis, cf. 72230

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72222. Non-residential building sales on a fee or contract basis
column5: Non-residential building sales on a fee or contract basis
column6: This subclass includes:- real estate agency and brokerage services related to the sale of non-residential buildings and associated land, such as offices, factories, hotels, shops, etc., and similar intermediation services involving buying, selling and renting of non-residential buildings and associated land, on a fee or contract basisThis subclass does not include:- sale of land on a fee or contract basis, cf. 72230

CPC21Code21ExplanatoryNote: 72223. Sale of time-share properties on a fee or contract basis
column5: Sale of time-share properties on a fee or contract basis
